f = FileUpload(BytesIO(to_bytes('a' * 256)), 'a.txt', 'a a a.txt', headers=
    {'Content-Type': 'text/plain', 'Content-Length': 256})
dstpath = '%s/%s' % (tempfile.mkdtemp(), f.name)
f.save(dstpath)
with open(dstpath, 'rb') as df:
    assert df.read() == to_bytes('a' * 256)
try:
    os.unlink(dstpath)
except:
    raise
